OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud mostly breaking up in the
OL,6,Fmorning with some sunny spells in the
OL,7,Fnorth, quite warm in Moray. Staying
OL,8,Fcloudier in Southern Aberdeenshire,
OL,9,Fthe cloud spreading north in the
OL,10,Fafternoon perhaps bringing a few
OL,11,Fpatches of rain, east coast cooler.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA cloudy evening with perhaps
OL,14,Fa little rain at times. The cloud
OL,15,Fbreaking up in the early hours with
OL,16,Fsome clear spells.
OL,17,
OL,18,CTuesday:FIt will be a dry day with
OL,19,Fsome long sunny spells through the
OL,20,Fday. Very warm with light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
