OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FWednesday will be sunny and very warm,
OL,7,Fperhaps some patchy coastal haar.
OL,8,FSunny, hot inland Thursday, coastal
OL,9,Fhaar, perhaps some thundery showers
OL,10,Flater. Showery on Friday.
